nodes.text: Cell block 923 was a prison cell block in the Varactyl Vale region of the Minimum Security Section, a sector of the Belsavis prison facility on the planet Belsavis. Two of the inmates incarcerated in cell block 923 were Amikab and the crime lord Ivory, and the block was overtaken by rioting during the invasion of Belsavis.
Cell block 923 is a class-restricted area on Belsavis in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, where the Smuggler class mission "Most Wanted" occurs.
